<note n="0609010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0609010">天竺三藏＝三藏法師【三】＊</note>
<note n="0609011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0609011">流＝留【元】【明】＊</note>
